**Professional Profile**
Nguyen Anh Tuan is an emerging professional in the information technology sector, demonstrating practical experience as a Tester on the Gimji Project, a restaurant management software. In this role, Tuan was responsible for analyzing SRS documents, developing comprehensive test plans and methods, and writing and modifying test cases. Key contributions included performing unit testing, verifying module interactions, preparing detailed test reports, and actively monitoring bug resolution by the development team. This experience showcases a strong foundational understanding of the software testing lifecycle despite having 0 years of formal professional experience.

**Core Skills & Technology**
Manual Testing, Test Case Writing, Test Plan Writing, Software Testing Life Cycle (STLC), Software Development Life Cycle (SDLC), Bug Reporting, SQL, Automation Fundamentals.

**Education & Certifications**
Nguyen Anh Tuan is currently pursuing a Bachelor's Degree in Computer Science from Ton Duc Thang University, with an expected graduation in 2025. Additionally, Tuan holds a 2023 B1 Preliminary - Aptis English (4 skills) Intermediate Level certification, demonstrating proficiency in English.